# MyTypist — Windsurf Rules (main app)

READ `../ai-rules/MASTER.md` (or `ai-rules/MASTER.md` from repo root) BEFORE WRITING ANY UI CODE.

## Project
- Stack: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite, raw CSS with CSS variables, Zustand, Motion, Swiper
- Code here in: `src/`
- Accent: `#6C47FF` | Currency: ₦ only | Mobile-first CSS

## Hard Banned
- Soft gradients, glassmorphism, oversized radii, pill overload
- 3-column equal feature cards
- `Inter` as default font
- Em-dashes (`—`), pure `#000`/`#fff`
- `window.addEventListener('scroll', ...)` for scroll
- Fake product UIs from `<div>` rectangles

## What Good Looks Like
Linear, Raycast, Stripe, GitHub — honest, functional.
- Buttons: 8-10px radius, solid fill
- Cards: 8-12px radius, 1px border, subtle shadow
- Transitions: 100-200ms ease

## Installed
- `motion` → `import { motion } from "motion/react"`
- `swiper` → `import { Swiper, SwiperSlide } from 'swiper/react'`

